OL,7,FA man who subjected a woman to an
OL,8,F'horrific' attack in which he poured
OL,9,Fboiling water over her, repeatedly
OL,10,Fkicked her and ripped her hair out,
OL,11,Fhas been jailed for eight years.
OL,13,FRichard Piercy, aged 35, of Lansdown
OL,14,FRoad, Faringdon, was sentenced after
OL,15,Fbeing convicted of inflicting
OL,16,Fgrievous bodily harm at Oxford Crown
OL,17,FCourt on 14 August.
OL,19,FPiercy was also made subject to an
OL,20,Findefinite restraining order.
